"processing for everyone. *Nat Methods* 17, 5–6 (2020). "
"[(DOI)](https://doi.org/10.1038/s41592-019-0650-1)"
msgstr ""
"Haase, R., Royer, L.A., Steinbach, P. et al. CLIJ: procesamiento de imágenes"
" acelerado en la GPU para todos. *Nat Methods* 17, 5-6 (2020). "
